---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - Rohit Kumar">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="w-48 h-48 mx-auto mb-6 rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-primary">
        <img
          src="/Rohit.jpeg"
          alt="Rohit Kumar"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
        />
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Me</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Hi! I'm Rohit Kumar, a passionate developer and tech enthusiast. I love building things for the web
        and sharing my knowledge with others through my blog and social media.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">My Journey</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        I started my journey in tech several years ago and have been continuously learning and growing since then.
        My experience spans across various technologies and frameworks, allowing me to build robust and scalable solutions.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">What I Do</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 space-y-2 mb-6">
        <li>Web Development</li>
        <li>Technical Writing</li>
        <li>Open Source Contributions</li>
        <li>Community Building</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        I'm always excited to connect with fellow developers and tech enthusiasts. Feel free to reach out to me
        through any of my social media channels or via email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>